div.p:
Extent should be specified for the works wherever possible;
  obligatory for works with digital text provided, after the edition
  statement:

References to these witnesses can be done with a link directly to a
  witness's or a listWit's
  @xml:id like in LIT2317Senodo and LIT1709Kebran.

